00:22:45.530 --> 00:22:46.800
[GOKU]
Hey! It's me, Goku!

00:22:46.900 --> 00:22:48.703
With the kids learning
to master Fusion,

00:22:48.803 --> 00:22:50.339
there's a light at
the end of the tunnel.

00:22:50.439 --> 00:22:53.078
Wait, what's that?
Why is the sky getting dark?

00:22:53.179 --> 00:22:56.586
[KIBITO] Supreme Kai, it's a
miracle you're still alive!

00:22:56.686 --> 00:22:58.055
[SUPREME KAI]
Kibito, let's move out!

00:22:58.155 --> 00:22:59.324
We must save Gohan!

00:22:59.424 --> 00:23:01.563
[GOKU] Next time,
on Dragon Ball Z Kai:

00:23:01.663 --> 00:23:05.336
"Found! A Faint Ray of Hope!
Awaken, Warriors!"

00:23:05.436 --> 00:23:06.939
[GOHAN] We're coming
for you, Majin Buu!

00:23:07.039 --> 00:23:09.544
You're gonna be sorry
you messed with our world!

